devdoc.details: This is a sample contract that combines a lot of features. This contract and its dependencies serve to demonstrate how those features work and how they are implemented. Features include: - ERC20 and DEX / Pancakeswap      - Adding and removing liquidity from a DEX      - Selling and buying tokens from a DEX      - Enabling and disabling those functions - Context - Ownable - Pausable - Whitelist / Blacklist - Mint and Burn - Taxes (also add to DEX LP) - Dividends (also in combination with a DEX) - Reflections - Timers - Vesting - Payment Splitting? - Voting - Roles - NFTs - Blind Auction - Permission to third parties - Flash Minting - Snapshots - Upgradable - Cross chain
